    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years, so it's ready to hit the road for many more adventures. Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out on a weekend getaway, this car is super reliable and still looks great in the driveway. It runs like a charm and is just waiting for its next owner to take the wheel. I'd love for you to come by, check it out, and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
