    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the high-strung S54 B32 power plant, delivering 333 hp through individual throttle bodies and a dual-overhead-cam valvetrain. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a 3.64 ratio limited-slip M-Differential. Mechanical highlights include a documented Vanos bulletproofing and rear subframe reinforcement\u2014critical preventative measures for this platform's longevity. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a recent suspension refresh including trailing arm bushings (RTABs) and front control arm bushings (FCABs). While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the compression remains optimal across all cylinders and the throttle response is razor-sharp. A performance-oriented example ready for the enthusiast who values mechanical integrity and a linear 8,000 RPM power band.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
