    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Experience the perfect blend of performance and reliability with this exceptionally well-cared-for vehicle. The exterior retains a brilliant shine, showing only the lightest signs of careful use, while the alloy wheels remain crisp and curbing-free. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free interior featuring plush, well-preserved seating and an intuitive infotainment system that functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, having benefited from regular oil changes and all scheduled maintenance, resulting in a smooth, quiet ride and confident braking. Every button works, every light shines, and the engine purrs with the steady rhythm of a machine that has been truly respected. It is a complete, honest package for a discerning buyer looking for a vehicle that looks as good as it drives.",
      "price": 36500.0,
