      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It's super reliable and still looks great parked in the driveway. If you're looking for a smooth, dependable car that's ready for its next adventure, this is the one! Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
