      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of BMW\u2019s S54-powered icon. The 3.2L straight-six breathes through individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power to a 6-speed manual transmission. Key enthusiast concerns have been addressed, including VANOS servicing and rear subframe reinforcement. The limited-slip differential and refreshed suspension bushings provide the analog feedback and lateral grip expected of the M-division's finest. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains tight and the engine pulls vigorously to the 8,000 RPM redline. A turn-key performer for the serious driver.",
